Package alix.util

Class IntVector

java.lang.Object
alix.util.IntList
alix.util.IntVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<IntList>
public class IntVector
extends IntList
A mutable list of ints with useful metadata, for example to calculate average. This object is not protected, for fast acess to fields, be careful to enjoy speed. Not suitable as a key for a hash (mutable).
Author:
glorieux-f
